<h1><span id="Scandinavian_Defence">Scandinavian Defence</span></h1>
<p>Black tries to avoid losing the lead in development. White can play to keep a material advantage (3. c4) or to build back a pawn center (3. d4). 3. Bb5+ gains time and can serve many purposes.
